Posts.Content: Jul 23, 2013 07:00PM Kiranoel wrote: I do not have cancer, but have had shooting paints, joint pain, swelling feet and neuropathy. My feet and hands were very numb. After six weeks of jin shin my tingling is gone and my feet are waking up. My pain is also gone and burning is minimal. Jin shin is a god send!
Posts.Title: Jin Shin Jyutsu (accupressure) stopped my neuropathy radiant Kiranoel
